<Algorithm code="         1. Assert: _intrinsicDefaultProto_ is this specification's name of an intrinsic object. The corresponding object must be an intrinsic that is intended to be used as the [[Prototype]] value of an object.         1. Let _proto_ be ? Get(_constructor_, *&#34;prototype&#34;*).         1. If _proto_ is not an Object, then           1. Let _realm_ be ? GetFunctionRealm(_constructor_).           1. Set _proto_ to _realm_'s intrinsic object named _intrinsicDefaultProto_.         1. Return _proto_.       ">
